{"tid":2233740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羈留者絕食百日獲聲援","createTime":"2020-10-07T10:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T11:07:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"179e43522b71aeeacbccd8ad31f059533d7751bf","tid":2233740,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/L2PYHPKYBZBW3KEZ6PQETDR5H4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FL2PYHPKYBZBW3KEZ6PQETDR5H4%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=67c996ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FL2PYHPKYBZBW3KEZ6PQETDR5H4%2F&h=22fe2828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/L2PYHPKYBZBW3KEZ6PQETDR5H4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n羈留者絕食百日獲聲援<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IIlN8yLie3S2PPVwIHdMi6cgvNE=/1944x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JGB3JNQSKZGWRBN4O7I6R4X3XU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIIlN8yLie3S2PPVwIHdMi6cgvNE%3D%2F1944x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJGB3JNQSKZGWRBN4O7I6R4X3XU.jpg&h=98568a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■聲援者手持燭光高呼口號。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】屯門青山灣入境事務中心（CIC）多名被羈留人士6月底起絕食，抗議入境處無限期羈留，至昨日已達100天，尚有七人堅持絕食。CIC關注組昨晚舉行聲援集會，支持被羈留人士。<br />\n<br />\n屯門青山灣入境事務中心用作接收逾期居留人士，6月底起，多名羈留者不滿被長期羈留發起絕食，要求盡快獲釋。一直協助他們的CIC關注組昨晚在中心外舉行聲援晚會，逾40人參與，包括立法會議員張超雄、邵家臻及被羈留者家人。他們手持燭光排成「FREE」字，希望被羈留人士可盡早與家人團聚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n環境惡劣 獲釋無期<br />\n<br />\n集會期間，中心內不斷傳出被羈留人士的叫喊聲，並高呼口號回應聲援者。關注組成員指，至今仍有七人繼續絕食，他們在這100天體重下降18公斤或以上。關注組亦批評中心環境惡劣，並收到被羈留人士投訴，未得到適當藥物治療，部份人只獲派止痛藥了事。<br />\n<br />\n張超雄表示，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n關注組原希望以人鏈組成「Free」字，惟被一批身穿便服的疑似警員以限聚令為由阻止，又以攝影機拍攝現場。"},{"pid":"220257c52c87bc4ab95676a240644fc8fe6ad4e9","tid":2233740,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"非法入境者要求盡快獲釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}